:11:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59009</s:story_id></item><item><title>WVU Splits Squads at Bryan Clay Invitational, Mountaineer Showcase</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/15/track-field-wvu-splits-squads-at-bryan-clay-invitational-mountaineer-showcase</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/15/track-field-wvu-splits-squads-at-bryan-clay-invitational-mountaineer-showcase</guid><category>Track &amp; Field</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Cate Pickering" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/15/DSC01497.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University track and field team splits action this weekend, competing at the Bryan Clay Invitational in Azusa, California, April 16-18, while also hosting the Mountaineer Showcase in Morgantown, April 17.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/15/DSC01497.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/15/DSC01497.jpg"><media:title>Cate Pickering</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/15/DSC01497.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 16:13:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>16</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59008</s:story_id></item><item><title>Harrison Named to CSC Academic All-America Third Team</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/15/womens-basketball-harrison-named-to-csc-academic-all-america-third-team</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/15/womens-basketball-harrison-named-to-csc-academic-all-america-third-team</guid><category>Women's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Jordan Harrison" src="https://admin